graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator (DSPO)"
        Controller[DSPO Controller]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "User-Defined Namespace - DSPA Instance"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>8887/TCP gRPC]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        WorkflowController[Argo Workflow Controller<br/>Namespace-scoped]
        MariaDB[(MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP)]
        Minio[(Minio<br/>9000/TCP)]
        MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP]
        MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP]
        UI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|deploys| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MariaDB
    Controller -->|deploys optional| Minio
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MLMDgRPC
    Controller -->|deploys optional| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|deploys optional| UI

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    APIServer -->|tracks lineage| MLMDgRPC
    APIServer -->|creates| ArgoWorkflow[Argo Workflow CR]

    WorkflowController -->|watches| ArgoWorkflow
    WorkflowController -->|creates| PipelinePods[Pipeline Step Pods]

    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|watches| ArgoWorkflow

    ScheduledWorkflow -->|creates scheduled| ArgoWorkflow

    PipelinePods -->|reads/writes artifacts| Minio
    PipelinePods -->|logs metadata| MLMDgRPC

    MLMDgRPC -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        ExternalDB[(External Database<br/>3306/TCP)]
        ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/manages| K8sAPI
    WorkflowController -->|orchestrates via| K8sAPI
    PipelinePods -->|pulls images from| ContainerRegistry

    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalS3
    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalDB
    PipelinePods -.->|optional| ExternalS3

    subgraph "ODH Integrations"
        ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        KServe[KServe]
        Ray[Ray]
    end

    ODHDashboard -->|UI integration| APIServer
    APIServer -->|can deploy| KServe
    APIServer -->|can deploy| Ray

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623
    style MariaDB fill:#e8e8e8
    style Minio fill:#e8e8e8
    style K8sAPI fill:#999
    style ExternalS3 fill:#999
    style ExternalDB fill:#999
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#999
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321
    style KServe fill:#7ed321
    style Ray fill:#7ed321
